Patient Navigation

Source: R/mod_navigation.R
mod_navigation.Rd

This module will render the datatable on the 'Patient Search' tab containing all patients in the cohort. The selected patient in the DT is kept in sync with the 'Chart Review' tab.

navigation_message(id)

mod_navigation_server(
  id,
  database_vars,
  datamodel_vars,
  abstract_vars,
  parent_session
)

Arguments

id

The namespace id for the UI output
database_vars

Database variables returned from user selected database setup module
datamodel_vars

Datamodel variables returned from mod_datamodel_setup
abstract_vars

Abstraction variables returned from user selected abstraction module
parent_session

the parent environment of this module
